Project basis and credits:

The public Land of Light fan gate page is based on the Retro web interface
project by Andrew Polk / Polklabs:

https://github.com/polklabs/stargate-retro

Land of Light adds its own public fan gate configuration, access restrictions,
session protection, browser audio, visual changes, and Land of Light-specific
behavior.

Permitted use:

- You may use the published Land of Light gate page to manually dial and test
  your own StargateProject-compatible gate.
- You may read this repository for personal reference.

Prohibited use:

- You may not modify, clone, mirror, impersonate, or republish the Land of Light
  public gate address or public gate page as if it were your own.
- You may not use the Land of Light public gate address for automated dialing,
  scraping, scanning, stress testing, denial-of-service testing, vulnerability
  probing, or any activity intended to interfere with the gate or network.
- You may not attempt to bypass access controls, authentication, rate limits,
  network protections, Cloudflare protections, or any other security mechanism.
- You may not attempt to access private pages, administrator controls, logs,
  configuration pages, local network resources, cameras, or services that were
  not intentionally published for guest use.
- You may not use this repository or the public gate address for hacking,
  exploitation, malware, credential harvesting, or unauthorized access.

No warranty:

The public gate page and any information in this repository are provided "as is"
without warranty of any kind. Availability is not guaranteed.

Termination:

Access to the public gate may be changed, limited, blocked, or removed at any
